set(CPACK_DEBIAN_PACKAGE_DESCRIPTION
"A Tunneler re-implementation, written with SDL.
 TunnelTanks is a modernized version of the 1991 DOS game 'Tunneler' by Geoffrey
 Silverton. It maintains much of the original graphical style, but brings in a
 richer color palette, several level generators, AI tanks, and a completely open
 code base.")
